data.description: Amazing 2 bed/2 bath condo steps from brown line stop on quiet tree lined street in Albany Park! Condo features: Amazing open floor plan, Tons of windows for great natural light, Hardwood floors throughout, Stainless steel appliances, Fireplace, In-unit laundry, Cute outdoor porch area in back, & HUGE 5x6x9 storage locker! Walk to shopping, public transportation and restaurants!!
